column5: Any one know of any tackle stores in the Scarborough area?

Any one know of any tackle stores in the Scarborough area?  There are three along Sheppard Avenue.  AV Fishing Tackle at Sheppard & Shorting, Lucky's at Sheppard & Midland, and a new one on the south side of Sheppard near Brimley.
also Pro J Tackle on Sheppard Ave,  east of Warden on the south side.
Pro J, south east corner of warden and sheppard, great store, lots of high end gear that nobody else sells
I think Pro J even has a no tax sale going on or did.  It was an "after the show sale" as they like to go to all the fishing shows.
Pro j will be doing the sportsman show and after the annual sale instore will happen again this year. no details yet, i will update when i do the list.
Pro J, south east corner of warden and sheppard, great store, lots of high end gear that nobody else sells store is on sheppard one block east of Warden on the south side, great store
